      • setScale

        public void setScale(double scale)
        クラスからコピーされた説明: OctaveGenerator
        Sets the scale used for all coordinates passed to this generator.

        This is the equivalent to setting each coordinate to the specified value.

        オーバーライド:
        setScale クラス内 OctaveGenerator
        パラメータ:
        scale - New value to scale each coordinate by

                    double z,
                    double w,
                    double frequency,

        Generates noise for the 3D coordinates using the specified number of octaves and parameters
        パラメータ:
        x - X-coordinate
        y - Y-coordinate

        w - W-coordinate

      • noise

        public double noise(double x,
                    double y,
                    double z,
                    double w,
                    double frequency,
                    double amplitude,
                    boolean normalized)
        Generates noise for the 3D coordinates using the specified number of octaves and parameters
        パラメータ:
        x - X-coordinate
        y - Y-coordinate
        z - Z-coordinate
        w - W-coordinate
        frequency - How much to alter the frequency by each octave
        amplitude - How much to alter the amplitude by each octave
        normalized - If true, normalize the value to [-1, 1]
        戻り値:
        Resulting noise
